---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="ChoreQuest — Privacy Policy" description="ChoreQuest privacy policy. Your family's data stays private.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <!-- Back link -->
    <a href="/" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white text-sm transition mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Privacy Policy — ChoreQuest for Families</h1>
    <p class="text-white/30 mb-10">Last updated: March 12, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">ChoreQuest is a family chore tracking app developed by Justin Bundrick / BunjiSolutions. Your privacy matters. Here's exactly what we do and don't do with your data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data We Collect</h2>
    
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Data Stored On Your Device</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Family name, member names, and parent PIN</li>
      <li>Chore definitions and completion history</li>
      <li>Reward definitions and redemption history</li>
      <li>Points, streaks, and challenge progress</li>
      <li>Photos taken for chore verification (stored locally only)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Data Synced via iCloud</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed">ChoreQuest uses Apple's iCloud (CloudKit) to sync family data across your devices. This includes:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Family name, member names, and family join code</li>
      <li>Chore assignments and completion records</li>
      <li>Reward definitions and redemption records</li>
      <li>Parent PIN (stored securely in your private iCloud container)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white/90">Apple manages iCloud security and encryption.</strong> We never see, access, or store your iCloud data on our servers. We have no servers.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Data We Do NOT Collect</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Email addresses</li>
      <li>Phone numbers</li>
      <li>Location data</li>
      <li>Browsing history</li>
      <li>Advertising identifiers</li>
      <li>Analytics or crash reports sent to us</li>
      <li>Any data shared with third parties</li>
      <li>Financial or banking information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Children's Privacy (COPPA)</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed">ChoreQuest is designed for family use, including children under 13. We comply with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA):</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">No account creation required.</strong> No email, no sign-up.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">No personal information collected from children.</strong> Names entered by parents stay on-device and in the family's private iCloud.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">No third-party tracking.</strong> Zero analytics SDKs, zero ad networks.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">No social features.</strong> No chat, no messaging, no public profiles.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white/90">Parents control all data.</strong> Parents can delete the family and all associated data at any time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed">All data is stored on your device and in your iCloud account. To delete all data:</p>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-white/60 mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Delete the app from your device</li>
      <li>Remove ChoreQuest data from iCloud (Settings → Apple ID → iCloud → Manage Storage)</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">We retain nothing. When you delete it, it's gone.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white/90">Apple iCloud (CloudKit):</strong> Used for family sync across devices. Subject to <a href="https://www.apple.com/privacy/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">Apple's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">No other third-party services are used. No analytics. No ads. No tracking.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">In-App Purchases</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">ChoreQuest is a one-time purchase ($6.99) processed entirely through Apple's App Store. We do not collect or have access to your payment information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">If we update this policy, we'll update the "Last updated" date above. Continued use of ChoreQuest after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:bunjisolutions@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition">bunjisolutions@gmail.com</a></p>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/10 mt-12 pt-8 text-center text-white/30 text-sm">
      <p>BunjiSolutions · Perry, Georgia</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
